Nicolle Dickson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicolle_Dickson 0 Nicolle Dickson (born 29 January 1969) is a former Australian actress, who was best known for playing the original character of teenage tearaway Bobby Simpson in soap opera Home and Away from 1988 to 1993. She left the acting career and is now an accountant and bookkeeper.
